{"image_id": "HAL_2007_page_15", "image_size": [1257, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "2007 ANNUAL REPORT    HALLIBURTON", "bbox": [1029.0, 1565.5, 1184.2, 1576.0]}, {"text": "13", "bbox": [1204.0, 1557.1, 1219.5, 1577.9]}, {"text": "Web site access", "bbox": [215.8, 111.7, 353.0, 132.6]}, {"text": "Our annual reports on Form 10-K, quarterly reports on Form 10-Q, current reports on Form 8-K, and", "bbox": [215.8, 138.5, 1062.2, 159.4]}, {"text": "amendments to those reports filed or furnished pursuant to Section 13(a) or 15(d) of the Exchange Act of 1934 are", "bbox": [140.7, 165.5, 1099.6, 186.4]}, {"text": "made available free of charge on our internet web site at www.halliburton.com as soon as reasonably practicable", "bbox": [140.7, 192.6, 1084.7, 213.5]}, {"text": "after we have electronically filed the material with, or furnished it to, the Securities and Exchange Commission", "bbox": [140.7, 219.8, 1073.2, 240.6]}, {"text": "(SEC).  The public may read and copy any materials we have filed with the SEC at the SEC’s Public Reference", "bbox": [140.7, 246.8, 1075.0, 267.6]}, {"text": "Room at 100 F Street, NE, Room 1580, Washington, DC 20549.  Information on the operation of the Public", "bbox": [140.7, 273.9, 1046.4, 294.8]}, {"text": "Reference Room may be obtained by calling the SEC at 1-800-SEC-0330.  The SEC maintains an internet site that", "bbox": [140.7, 301.0, 1101.8, 321.9]}, {"text": "contains our reports, proxy and information statements, and our other SEC filings.  The address of that site is", "bbox": [140.7, 328.0, 1054.3, 348.9]}, {"text": "www.sec.gov.  We have posted on our web site our Code of Business Conduct, which applies to all of our", "bbox": [140.7, 355.2, 1030.1, 376.1]}, {"text": "employees and Directors and serves as a code of ethics for our principal executive officer, principal financial officer,", "bbox": [140.7, 382.3, 1120.3, 403.2]}, {"text": "principal accounting officer, and other persons performing similar functions.  Any amendments to our Code of", "bbox": [140.7, 409.3, 1068.2, 430.2]}, {"text": "Business Conduct or any waivers from provisions of our Code of Business Conduct granted to the specified officers", "bbox": [140.7, 436.4, 1113.5, 457.3]}, {"text": "above are disclosed on our web site within four business days after the date of any amendment or waiver pertaining", "bbox": [140.7, 463.6, 1109.2, 484.4]}, {"text": "to these officers.  There have been no waivers from provisions of our Code of Business Conduct during 2007, 2006,", "bbox": [140.7, 490.6, 1113.0, 511.4]}, {"text": "or 2005.", "bbox": [140.7, 517.7, 215.5, 538.6]}, {"text": "Item 1(a).  Risk Factors.", "bbox": [140.7, 572.3, 361.6, 593.2]}, {"text": "Information related to risk factors is described in “Management’s Discussion and Analysis of Financial", "bbox": [215.8, 599.0, 1082.1, 619.9]}, {"text": "Condition and Results of Operations” under “Forward-Looking Information and Risk Factors.”", "bbox": [140.7, 626.1, 940.1, 647.0]}, {"text": "Item 1(b).  Unresolved Staff Comments.", "bbox": [140.7, 680.7, 494.2, 701.6]}, {"text": "None.", "bbox": [215.8, 707.4, 271.6, 728.3]}, {"text": "Item 2.  Properties.", "bbox": [140.7, 762.0, 316.9, 782.9]}, {"text": "We own or lease numerous properties in domestic and foreign locations.  The following locations represent", "bbox": [215.8, 788.7, 1116.2, 809.5]}, {"text": "our major facilities and corporate offices.", "bbox": [140.7, 815.7, 491.0, 836.5]}, {"text": "Location", "bbox": [174.2, 871.8, 245.7, 890.6]}, {"text": "Owned/Leased", "bbox": [529.1, 871.8, 646.5, 890.6]}, {"text": "Description", "bbox": [670.1, 871.8, 762.5, 890.6]}, {"text": "Operations:", "bbox": [195.9, 900.4, 287.5, 919.2]}, {"text": "Completion and Production segment:", "bbox": [212.1, 927.0, 499.1, 945.7]}, {"text": "Carrollton, Texas", "bbox": [248.4, 954.1, 384.4, 972.9]}, {"text": "Owned", "bbox": [529.2, 954.1, 583.5, 972.9]}, {"text": "Manufacturing facility", "bbox": [670.3, 954.1, 844.3, 972.9]}, {